    list_recordsets(schema_name, recordset_type)

    list_recordsets.Rd

    return a list of tables and views available in PSRC's in-house data warehouse

    Usage

    list_recordsets(schema_name = "", include_base_tables = FALSE)

    Arguments

    schema_name

    (string, optional) If supplied, this limits the returned list to only those tables and views in schema_name.

    include_base_tables

    (TRUE|FALSE, optional) If false, return only the views (no tables). False is the default.

    Value

    a list of tables, in the form of a dataframe
